{
  "version": 1,
  "principles": [
    "Do not call paid/free-quota APIs from frontend rendering.",
    "Use StatsBomb Open Data for advanced historical features where coverage exists.",
    "Use OpenFootball for broad schedules/results when a verified source exists.",
    "Use API-Football only as an operational cache warmer for gaps and current competitions.",
    "If a league has only score/calendar coverage, build GOUP metrics from results and form instead of inventing advanced stats."
